The harvester and the ambulance were heading to Arnot from Hendrina while the truck was driving from the Arnot direction. The accident happened underneath a bridge. According to a passer-by, the bridge was too narrow for both the truck and harvester to drive through. The ambulance was on its way to an accident scene in Arnot when the incident happened. The two paramedics sustained minor injuries, the driver of the harvester was unharmed.